name: Pan(them)ya!
description:
[Trigger warning: Self-harm]

Pan(them)ya! was first shown to Art Rally MNL’s 𝓨𝓸𝓾 = 𝓤 - an online event to remind those who are battling HIV/AIDS that YOU are loved, YOU are important, and YOU are not alone.

For transparency, sales from this piece will be going to the Aeta Community (groceries and school supplies), and the Filipino’s affected by Typhoon Odette.
